body:
### Welcome to Sentiments Express GitHub!
Sentiments Express one of the top online Gifts website in Pakistan where you can buy for yourself or you can send to your loved ones or relatives through Sentiments Express. Sentiments Express also covering different types of events like Valentine's Day Gifts, Mother's Day Gifts, Father's Day Gifts, Mango Tango, EID Day, Halloween Gifts, Christmas Event, Happy New Year season etc.

### eCommerce Website!
[Amazon](http://amazon.com) & [eBay](http://ebay.com) are the very popular & well named online eCommerce platform in the world.

### Send Gifts to Pakistan!
We are covering more than 225 countries from where you can send [Gifts to Pakistan](http://sentimentsexpress.com) like United States, United Kingdom, United Arab Emirates, Canada, Australia, etc. [Send Cakes to Pakistan](http://sentimentsexpress.com/cakes.html), [Send Flowers to Pakistan](http://sentimentsexpress.com/flowers.html)! 

### Top Categories!
* Cakes
* Flowers
* Perfumes
* Chocolates

### User Friendly Website!
Online Gifts Shopping & Gifts delivering website in Pakistan. The website exactly designed to be user friendly and easy to use. You can place order easily and get free delivered anywhere in Pakistan.
